@startuml
title Interactive Session — State Machine

[*] --> MenuDisplay : session starts

MenuDisplay --> OperationSelection : show numbered menu

OperationSelection --> OperationSelection : invalid index\n(re-prompt)
OperationSelection --> OperandInput : valid index selected

OperandInput --> OperandInput : invalid operand\n(ValueError — re-prompt)
OperandInput --> Execution : valid operand(s) provided

Execution --> ResultDisplay : success
Execution --> ResultDisplay : ZeroDivisionError\n("Error: Division by zero")
Execution --> ResultDisplay : other exception\n("Error: {exc}")

ResultDisplay --> ContinuePrompt : result printed

ContinuePrompt --> ContinuePrompt : unrecognised input\n(re-prompt)
ContinuePrompt --> MenuDisplay : yes / y
ContinuePrompt --> Exit : no / n

Exit --> [*]

@enduml
